<Title>Flight Deck Forward Window Primary Heat Channels (*)</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="A" nbrInstalled="2" nbrRequired="1">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One may be inoperative provided:</Para>
<List listType="a.">
<ListItem>
<Para>Associated switch remains off.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Associated forward window backup heat channel operates normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Side window heat channels operate normally.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>Airplane is not operated in known or forecast icing conditions.</Para>
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Para>EDTO beyond 120 minutes is not conducted</Para>
</ListItem>
</List>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<OperationNote>
<Para>If cracks are observed in the associated window, notify maintenance to inspect the window per AMM 56-11-00.</Para>
</OperationNote>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
